都唔同啦<br />\n以前會肯融入香港，講廣東話<br />\n依家？你望下堆新移民幾撚聲大夾惡用普通話屌返你轉頭<br />\n<br />\n反還反，用下腦而唔係盲反，做人要有批判性思考<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：土生土長香港人，唔洗話我支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66ef40f397856997c82fff0bb65c0895c107f07","tid":215850,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T18:27:51.000Z","msg":"邊個冚家產娶件咁嘅大陸婆落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0deeaf064eef298c5c2658d17531e70ab80d381","tid":215850,"uid":11261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T19:03:38.000Z","msg":"仆街，竟然有人去幫條支那婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e5fe381b7f73acc7f06931d4e030905dbab7cc","tid":215850,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T23:01:11.000Z","msg":"垃圾人種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe2dc6a050ae1226d8e91dc9e552377f98ae18a","tid":215850,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T23:08:30.000Z","msg":"返中國啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5fba15ee8ac29d5f218753f5228311ac955a2c3","tid":215850,"uid":67231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T23:29:02.000Z","msg":"食屎啦 唔識教仔仲駁咀"},{"pid":"f8bb75c5f3fe06be0ef1e33e745bf7b13a4ce907","tid":215850,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T23:38:30.000Z","msg":"契丹人返支那"},{"pid":"b117ed0a022fa4090c073bde3080a07164890a28","tid":215850,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T23:50:31.000Z","msg":"嘈又嘈得最大聲 之後又扮曬委屈 咁好演技去拍戲支那蝗"},{"pid":"dc4e2bcd375d9e54eb9ccdc5fd18b7fdbf5dfe3f","tid":215850,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T00:01:01.000Z","msg":"女人嘈唔贏最識扮喊"},{"pid":"92326045d7f8eab60269fe43621bd556b56ddbd1","tid":21